item.title: Help me i have 2 problems
item.dc:creator: @kicker862 kicker862
item.description:
@kicker862 wrote:

miked27dd:

and when i changed the 127.00.1 to my no-ip it doesn’t let me log in now on my own so i need help connecting my server threw my no-ip

You dont connect with your no-ip.
That is for others to connect.
You have to release your client download with your no-ip in use.
And then on your side you have to change your no-ip back to localhost.
